Hello, thank you for contacting Melody Harmony Music School. My name is Daniel Simmons. May I know your name, please?

Hi Daniel, my name is Theresa Jenkins.

Nice to meet you, Theresa. How can I assist you today?

I'm a bit disappointed because the music book I ordered hasn't arrived yet.

I'm sorry to hear that, Theresa. Could you please provide your order number so I can check the status for you?

Sure, the order number is one two three four five.

Thank you. I see here that the shipment was delayed. Can you confirm your shipping address, Theresa?

Yes, it's two three five Oak Street, Apt two zero two.

Thank you for confirming. I’ll make sure your order is prioritized. It should reach you within the next three days.

I appreciate that, Daniel. Thanks for your help.

You're welcome, Theresa. Thank you for your patience and understanding. If you have any further questions, feel free to contact us. Have a great day!
